>> title: The Siesta
>> source: https://recipe.awesomedrinks.com/recipe/the-siesta/

Add @blanco Tequila{60%ml}, @Campari{15%ml}, @fresh grapefruit juice{15%ml} , @fresh lime juice{15%ml}, @simple syrup{22.5%ml} over @ice into a #cocktail shaker{}

